, "experiences/5/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/5/jobStartedOn": "11-2019", "experiences/5/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/5/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/5/title": "General Manager, Mövenpick Ambassador Hotel Accra", "experiences/6/companyId": "18623803", "experiences/6/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/6/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/mp-hotels-group/", "experiences/6/companyName": "Meeting Point Hotels", "experiences/6/companySize": "1001-5000", "experiences/6/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:18623803", "experiences/6/companyWebsite": "https://www.mphotels.com/", "experiences/6/jobDescription": "Founded by Meeting Point International, part of the FTI Group, in September 2015, MP Hotels is an international hospitality company with a portfolio of five brands comprising more than 80 properties with more than 16,000 rooms, in 12 countries and 4 continents. Every hotel or resort is built directly by or in close proximity to the beach and offers guests a wide variety of dining options, complimentary Wi-Fi and friendly hospitality services. The company’s portfolio includes LABRANDA Hotels & Resorts with its five sub brands that include select, comfort, balance, family star and city, Design Plus Hotels, Kairaba Hotels & Resorts, Club Sei and Lemon & Soul Hotels. Located in sunny destinations, by the beach or in close proximity to the beach, Meeting Point Hotels is dedicated to serve guests hospitality with a smile and deliver authentic experiences with a local flair. Couples, singles and families, whether sun-seekers, sports fanatics or experience and culturally driven, our wide hotel range has just the right choice for everyone. The resorts and hotels are distributed from Cuba, the Canary Islands, The Gambia, Morocco, Malta, Italy, Croatia and Cyprus, Greece to Turkey, Egypt and Oman. Our guests get pampered through their brand of choice.\n\nMP Hotels currently have 13 existing and 4 upcoming hotels in Turkey.", "experiences/6/jobEndedOn": "8-2019", "experiences/6/jobLocation": "Turkey", "experiences/6/jobLocationCountry": "DE", "experiences/6/jobStartedOn": "1-2019", "experiences/6/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/6/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E0BAQFdMbyDUZPqQw/company-logo_400_400-alternative/company-logo_400_400-alternative/0/1630633870939/mp_hotels_group_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=BfZi_8LYe1liDak9n8zPZJyrnyC1eiySwBM74KbtBHw", "experiences/6/title": "Chief Operating Officer", "experiences/7/companyId": "3055", "experiences/7/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/7/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/7/companyName": "AccorHotels", "experiences/7/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/7/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/7/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/7/jobDescription": "Swissôtel Resort, Bodrum Beach lies directly on the waterfront in Turgutreis, approximately 20 km from the centre of Bodrum, a very popular destination as it offers ideal conditions for water sports, culture and Aegean relaxation.The main two-storey hotel of Swissotel Resort, Bodrum Beach comprises 66 luxury rooms and suites, with minimum 40 m² per room with 72 private residences.The restaurants and bars are places of entertainment, where the ambience runs from formal to casual and dishes are prepared with the best local products. With indoor & outdoor pools and Purovel Spa & Sport facilities, the resort provides you with a wide variety of sport and leisure opportunities.\n\nThe luxurious Bodrum city project Swissôtel Resort, Bodrum Hill is located in the hills of Yokusbasi, with a fascinating panoramic view over the city. 129 elegant rooms & suites and 35 private residences offer stylish contemporary design, cutting-edge technology and warm Swiss hospitality. Two restaurants guarantee top cuisine with quality ingredients and fresh products in a modern atmosphere, combined with heartfelt and impeccable service, and the bar is the perfect place to meet up for drinks with friends or colleagues. You can continue your fitness routine or revitalise with a treatment at Purovel Spa & Sport. Easily reached by car or taxi, the vibrant city centre of Bodrum, with its lively bars & restaurants, is 10 minutes from the hotel and the airport is just 20 minutes away. Opening in 2019.\n\nBoth hotels include Swissôtel Residences with luxurious villas.", "experiences/7/jobEndedOn": "10-2018", "experiences/7/jobLocation": "Bodrum, Turkey", "experiences/7/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/7/jobStartedOn": "3-2016", "experiences/7/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/7/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/7/title": "Cluster General Manager, Swissôtel Resort Bodrum Beach & Swissôtel Resort Bodrum Hill", "experiences/8/companyId": "3549", "experiences/8/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/8/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/ihghotels&resorts/", "experiences/8/companyName": "InterContinental Hotels Group (IHG®)", "experiences/8/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/8/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3549", "experiences/8/companyWebsite": "http://www.ihgplc.com", "experiences/8/jobDescription": "InterContinental Foshan provides 445 guest rooms, including Club InterContinental rooms and a range of suites. All of the rooms are finely appointed with beautiful views of the Qiandeng Lake or elegant landscaped garden for completing comfort and convenience.\n\nHotel is owned by Poly Commercial Real Estate Investment & Management Co., Ltd. a subsidiary of Poly Group, a State Owned Enterprise. \n\n“Certificate of Excellence 2014 Winner” by Tripadvisor |“2014年度卓越奖”到到网\n“Best Business Hotel” by <​Voyage> the 5th Best Hotel & Resort Valued Award | “最佳商务会奖酒店” 第五届《新旅行》年度高端酒店评选\n“Best MICE Hotel” by <​Travel & Leisure> 2013 Travel Awards | “最佳会议接待酒店” 《旅游休闲》2013 年度旅游大奖\n“The Best Guest Experience Business Hotel ” 2013 Fashion List Awards of China Hotel | “最佳宾客体验商务酒店”2013酒店风尚榜\n“Best Hotel in Central South China” The 6th Annual TTG China Travel Awards 2013 |“华南地区最佳酒店” 2013第六届年度TTG中国旅游大奖", "experiences/8/jobEndedOn": "3-2016", "experiences/8/jobLocation": "Foshan, Guangdong, China", "experiences/8/jobLocationCountry": "GB", "experiences/8/jobStartedOn": "5-2015", "experiences/8/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/8/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQE0llq6fMNiSA/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1719918902479/ihghotelsresorts_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=SQmjsK2eROVCLZpbMs_TGGjQDaoKOftZi4zpFZgMWdM", "experiences/8/title": "General Manager, InterContinental Foshan", "experiences/9/companyId": "16190152", "experiences/9/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/9/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/wanda-hotels-&-resorts/", "experiences/9/companyName": "Wanda Hotels & Resorts", "experiences/9/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/9/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:16190152", "experiences/9/companyWebsite": "http://www.wandahotels.com", "experiences/9/jobDescription": "Wanda Vista Dongguan is successfully opened on Friday, The September 12th, 2014\n\nThe hotel features 302 spacious guestrooms and suites with elegant design and deluxe decorations. There’s a variety of choices for food & beverage facilities, including the Café Vista, ZHEN-Chinese Restaurant and He Japanese restaurant, so no matter where you end up, every appetite for great dining and entertainment will be satisfied. \n\n3,000-square-meter Grand Ballroom and 7 function rooms of different sizes can cater to your special meeting or event. Offering a 1,400-square-meter pillar-less Grand Ballroom equipped with state-of-the-art technology, including a giant LED screen of over 105 square meters and one-stop “Executive Meeting Director” and “Wanda Romance Wedding Ceremony” services, Wanda Vista Dongguan promises to meet your every need.\n\n2014年金樽奖最值得期待新开业的奢华酒店 | The Most Anticipated Newly Opened Luxurious Hotels By Gold Champion Awards 2014 \n• 2014年金橄榄奖中国最值期待新开酒店 | The Most Anticipated New Opening Hotel of China by Golden-Olive Awards 2014 \n• 2014中国酒店风尚榜最值得期待新开奢华酒店 | The Most Anticipated New Opening Luxury Hotel by Fashion List Awards of China Hotel\n\nWanda Hotels and Resorts is China’s largest five-star hotel management company. The company currently owns 57 hotel properties across China as of June 2014, which includes properties it owns and leases as well as properties it owns and manages under its own hotel brands- the five-star Wanda Realm, the luxury five-star Wanda Vista and the super luxury five-star Wanda Reign. Wanda plans to become the world’s largest owner of 5 star hotels in 2015 by expanding its portfolio to 96 hotels and increasing total floor area to over 3 million square meters.", "experiences/9/jobEndedOn": "5-2015", "experiences/9/jobLocation": "Dongcheng, Dongguan, Guangdong, China", "experiences/9/jobStartedOn": "3-2014", "experiences/9/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/9/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E0BAQGwyQ0X9uH3Vg/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1630572356056/wanda_hotels__resorts_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=j8Wurdpz-0XHebUNsj6pYD5850tuNcLnUiAexL0yqyA", "experiences/9/title": "General Manager, Wanda Vista Dongguan", "experiences/10/companyId": "16190152", "experiences/10/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/10/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/wanda-hotels-&-resorts/", "experiences/10/companyName": "Wanda Hotels & Resorts", "experiences/10/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/10/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:16190152", "experiences/10/companyWebsite": "http://www.wandahotels.com", "experiences/10/jobDescription": "Wanda Hotels & Resorts Co., Ltd. is now the largest hotel owner in China. \n\nFounded in 2012, Wanda Hotels & Resorts aims to be a global leading operator of luxury Chinese hospitality brands as well as one of the world's outstanding hotel ownership and management companies. . \n\nWanda Hotels and Resorts Co Ltd has opened 51 five star and luxury five star hotels across China by December 23, 2013. At present, the company owns and manages 3 hotel brands- the five star Wanda Realm, the luxury five star Wanda Vista and the super luxury five star Wanda Reign. Wanda plans to become the world’s largest owner of 5 star hotels in 2015 by expanding its portfolio to 80 hotels and increasing total operating space to over 3 million square meters.\n\nDalian Wanda Group was founded in 1988 and operates in four major segments: commercial property, luxury hotels, culture & tourism, and department stores. The company has 300 billion yuan ($48 billion) in total assets, and 141.7 billion yuan ($22.7 billion) in annual revenue, 20.2 billion yuan in annual taxes, and net profit of more than 10 billion yuan. By December 23, 2013, Wanda Group increased its portfolio to 85 Wanda Plazas, 51 five-star and super five-star hotels, 1,247 movie screens, 75 department stores and 81 karaoke center.\n\nWanda Group acquired the entire stake of the world’s second biggest cinema chain AMC and inherited its debt with $2.6 billion. It is the largest acquisition made by a private Chinese company in the US and also the biggest overseas M&A in China’s culture industry. The merger made Wanda the world’s largest cinema operator. \n\nWanda announced to acquire a majority shareholding in UK luxury yacht manufacturer Sunseeker with GBP320 million and develop a real estate project in Central London, which will include a five-star luxury hotel, with a total investment value of GBP 700 million.", "experiences/10/jobEndedOn": "3-2014", "experiences/10/jobLocation": "Jiaocheng, Ningde, Fujian, China", "experiences/10/jobStartedOn": "3-2013", "experiences/10/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/10/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E0BAQGwyQ0X9uH3Vg/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1630572356056/wanda_hotels__resorts_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=j8Wurdpz-0XHebUNsj6pYD5850tuNcLnUiAexL0yqyA", "experiences/10/title": "General Manager, Wanda Realm Ningde", "experiences/11/companyId": "3055", "experiences/11/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/11/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/11/companyName": "Accor", "experiences/11/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/11/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/11/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/11/jobDescription": "2012 Voyage Gourmet Gold List (Beacon Restaurant) - Voyage Magazine\n\n2012 Certificate of Excellence – TripAdvisor.com\n\n2012 Best Hotel Restaurant (Beacon Restaurant) - Gold List Award of China Tourism\n\n2012 Top 10 Business Hotels  of China - The 7th China Hotel Starlight Award\n\n2011 The Best Luxury Business Hotel in Guangdong Hong Kong Macau - Golden Pearl Award\n\nPositioned on historic town, Humen, the Sofitel Dongguan Humen Oriental hotel’s 62 floors rise elegantly in the corridor of Guangzhou and Shenzhen. With extensive meeting facilities, business support services and free internet access, the hotel has 409 luxurious rooms, all with panoramic city view and above 53 square meters. Fascinating restaurants and lounges can be found on the hotel's highest floors. Stay fit with roof garden, tennis court, indoor pool and full gym, enjoy a Magnifique life.\n\nInteriors feature a soothing palette of fabrics and stone, respectfully blending elements of French design and Chinese tradition.  Sight lines are enhanced with floor to ceiling windows, and clever use of interior glass and mirrors. Dining venues are an eclectic mix, using rich fabrics and colours in the lounges, and earth materials of wood, water, stone and textured metals in the dining rooms.\n\nThe hotel’s 62 floors sit atop the Huanghe Commercial complex, in Humen Town, the heart of Dongguan’s garment and shipping district.  Dongguan is located in southern Guangdong Province, east of the Pearl River Delta. Roughly 50 kilometers south of Guangzhou, and 30 kilometers north of Shenzhen, Dongguan is also convenient by ferry, about 70 kilometers from Hong Kong and Macau.\n\nSofitel Dongguan Humen Oriental is no longer operated by Sofitel Luxury Hotels as of April 2013.", "experiences/11/jobEndedOn": "3-2013", "experiences/11/jobLocation": "Humen, Dongguan, Guangdong, China", "experiences/11/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/11/jobStartedOn": "10-2011", "experiences/11/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/11/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/11/title": "General Manager, Sofitel Dongguan Humen Oriental", "experiences/12/companyId": "3055", "experiences/12/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/12/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/12/companyName": "Accor", "experiences/12/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/12/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/12/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/12/jobDescription": "Successfully completed below certifications for Swissôtel Foshan by Swiss Association for Quality and Management Systems (SQS);\n\nISO 9001 Quality Management\nISO 14001 Environmental Management\nOHSAS 18001 Health & Safety Management\n\nSwissôtel Foshan is a five star luxury hotel catering to today's discerning modern business and leisure travellers. The first international luxury hotel in the city, Swissôtel Foshan aims to establish itself as an icon in the business community. The hotel symbolizes luxury, elegance and impeccable service.\n\nRising to the height of 208 metres, Swissôtel Foshan is the tallest building and a prominent landmark in Foshan. All 234 guest rooms and suites and 14 serviced apartments provide a graciously intimate and tranquil environment.\n\nSwissôtel Foshan is conveniently located near the Zumiao Commercial District and the Fenjiang Financial District, and is just minutes from Foshan Highway, an expressway linking Foshan to Guangzhou and Shunde.", "experiences/12/jobEndedOn": "10-2011", "experiences/12/jobLocation": "Chancheng, Foshan, Guangdong, China", "experiences/12/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/12/jobStartedOn": "12-2010", "experiences/12/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/12/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/12/title": "General Manager, Swissôtel Foshan", "experiences/13/companyId": "3055", "experiences/13/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/13/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/13/companyName": "Accor", "experiences/13/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/13/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/13/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/13/jobDescription": "Swissôtel Makkah, Swissôtel's first hotel to open in Saudi Arabia, offers 1562 luxurious rooms and suites, with their modern design complementing the values of the contemporary Arabian culture.\n\nA part of the prestigious Abraj Al Bait complex, the deluxe Swissôtel Makkah, which opens in summer 2012, is a contemporary five-star hotel located in close proximity to the holy Masjid Al Haraam, overlooking the Ka'aba and the Grand Mosque.\n\nWith a comprehensive array of facilities, Swissôtel Makkah is part of a new urban complex development. Boasting an all-under-one-roof concept, the hotel features 1562 contemporary guest rooms & luxury suites, three restaurants & one tea lounge, three meeting rooms and one business center.", "experiences/13/jobEndedOn": "12-2010", "experiences/13/jobLocation": "Makkah, Kingdom of Saudi Arabia", "experiences/13/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/13/jobStartedOn": "11-2009", "experiences/13/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/13/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/13/title": "General Manager, Swissôtel Makkah", "experiences/14/companyId": "3055", "experiences/14/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/14/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/14/companyName": "Accor", "experiences/14/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/14/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/14/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/14/jobDescription": "Swissôtel Göcek Marina Resort is located in the quiet and picturesque fishing village of Göcek. The natural bay makes Göcek an ideal destination for sailing and boating, and is the perfect place to relax. The hotel is set amongst lush Mediterranean gardens with wonderful views of the mountains. \n\nWith a choice of luxurious hotel accommodation, all the hotel rooms offer a private balcony or terrace featuring stunning views. Facilities include an outdoor pool, private beach, massage and beauty treatments and a wide variety of water sports, volleyball, cycling and facilities designed specifically for children.\n\nSwissôtel Göcek Marina Resort is no longer operated by Swissôtel Hotels & Resorts and currently managed by Dogus Group as D-Marin Resort Gocek (http://www.dresortgocek.com.tr/en/home.aspx)", "experiences/14/jobEndedOn": "5-2010", "experiences/14/jobLocation": "Gocek, Fethiye, Mugla, Turkiye", "experiences/14/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/14/jobStartedOn": "11-2009", "experiences/14/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/14/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/14/title": "General Manager, Swissôtel Göcek Marina & Resort", "experiences/15/companyId": "3055", "experiences/15/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/15/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/15/companyName": "Accor", "experiences/15/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/15/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/15/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/15/jobDescription": "Swissôtel Ankara, which has been awarded as one of the best Hotels in the world TOP 100 by Conde Nast Traveler readers, is a boutique-style five star hotel located in Çankaya, an exclusive area which is also closed to the Presidential Palace and many embassies.\n\nSwissôtel Ankara is a mere 45 minute drive from Esenboga airport and five minutes from the city centre and business district.\n\nOpened in April 2006, Swissôtel Ankara has many restaurants, bars, stores and shopping malls in the vicinity.", "experiences/15/jobEndedOn": "11-2009", "experiences/15/jobLocation": "Ankara, Turkey", "experiences/15/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/15/jobStartedOn": "11-2007", "experiences/15/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/15/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/15/title": "General Manager, Swissôtel Ankara", "experiences/16/companyId": "3055", "experiences/16/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/16/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/16/companyName": "Accor", "experiences/16/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/16/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/16/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/16/jobDescription": "Swissôtel Göcek Marina Resort is located in the quiet and picturesque fishing village of Göcek. The natural bay makes Göcek an ideal destination for sailing and boating, and is the perfect place to relax. The hotel is set amongst lush Mediterranean gardens with wonderful views of the mountains. \n\nWith a choice of luxurious hotel accommodation, all the hotel rooms offer a private balcony or terrace featuring stunning views. Facilities include an outdoor pool, private beach, massage and beauty treatments and a wide variety of water sports, volleyball, cycling and facilities designed specifically for children.\n\nSwissôtel Göcek Marina Resort is no longer operated by Swissôtel Hotels & Resorts and currently managed by Dogus Group as D-Marin Resort Gocek (http://www.dresortgocek.com.tr/en/home.aspx)", "experiences/16/jobEndedOn": "11-2007", "experiences/16/jobLocation": "Gocek, Fethiye, Mugla, Ankara", "experiences/16/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/16/jobStartedOn": "11-2006", "experiences/16/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/16/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/16/title": "General Manager, Swissôtel Göcek Marina & Resort", "experiences/17/companyId": "3354524", "experiences/17/companyIndustry": "Events Services", "experiences/17/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/icec-lutfi-kirdar-istanbul/", "experiences/17/companyName": "İstanbul Lütfi Kırdar / Istanbul Lutfi Kirdar - ICEC", "experiences/17/companySize": "51-200", "experiences/17/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3354524", "experiences/17/companyWebsite": "http://www.icec.org", "experiences/17/jobDescription": "The Istanbul Convention & Exhibition Centre (ICEC) has everthing you need to organize memorable and successful congresses and exhibitions in the imperial city of Istanbul. The only place in Istanbul where 3,500 delegates can sit down together for a five-star gala dinner, ICEC offers you an outstanding combination of state-of-the-art facilities and superior service.\n\nICEC's brand new Rumeli Fair & Exhibition Hall features Istanbul's largest Ballroom measuring 2,100 square meters, which includes simultaneous translation in eleven languages, full audio-visual support and more. The ballroom also divides easily into two smaller ballrooms using sound-proof seperators. For large receptions , the Ballroom can be combined with Rumeli's 1,100 square meter and 900 square meter foyers or the foyers can be used staging and registration areas.\n\nThe Anadolu Auditorium seats 2,000 in arm-chair comfort and offers complete technical facilities for even the most elaborate performances. From full 16 mm and 35 mm projection facilities to professionally tuned acoustics, the Anadolu Auditorium is a world-class event venue. It was here that world leaders, including Bill Clinton and Jacques Chirac, enjoyed a performance of the epic \"Lyrical History of Anatolia\", a stage extravaganza featuring a cast of more than 500 and sophisticated lighting, set changes and more. The Anadolu Auditorium was also the site of the Turkish launch of Windows 2000, featuring an address by Bill Gates, broadcast live by satellite up-link. \nBreak - out rooms, session rooms and satellite conferences \nNo matter how complicated your event is, ICEC has the infrastructure to meet your needs and ensure that your conference or trade fair runs smoothly.", "experiences/17/jobEndedOn": "11-2006", "experiences/17/jobLocation": "Sisli, Istanbul, Turkiye", "experiences/17/jobLocationCountry": "TR", "experiences/17/jobStartedOn": "8-2005", "experiences/17/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/17/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D0BAQEkmpOLUHJ2ZQ/company-logo_400_400/B4DZyydVUcJoAY-/0/1772520560722/icec_lutfi_kirdar_istanbul_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=rXMmMZvdAONDLdu0rSBfbeLZqsfjVnwf-MU9MvqKWWE", "experiences/17/title": "Deputy General Manager i/c of Sales&Marketing/Operations, ICEC", "experiences/18/companyId": "2449", "experiences/18/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/18/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/hilton/", "experiences/18/companyName": "Hilton", "experiences/18/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/18/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:2449", "experiences/18/companyWebsite": "http://stories.hilton.com", "experiences/18/jobDescription": "Hilton Adana\n\nWith Seyhan River views, the Adana HiltonSA hotel is just 5 minutes' drive from Adana Airport. Do business in one of 17 meeting rooms or the Executive Lounge, unwind in the health club or cool off in the 2 pools. \n\nTry international and Turkish cuisine in the Adana HiltonSA hotel's Chibo Restaurant, dine on the terrace at the Spice Market Restaurant or enjoy the late-night Zeytini Bar. \n\nEnjoy a Turkish bath or spinning class in the health club at the Adana HiltonSA hotel. Try the gym, tennis courts or the indoor and outdoor pools. Visit Adana attractions like Mavi Su Aqualand waterpark or Sabanci Mosque. \n\nFive minutes from Adana Sakirpasa Airport, the Adana HiltonSA hotel has 17 meeting rooms for 8-1000, an Executive Lounge and a business center with wireless internet access. All rooms have high-speed internet access. Step up to a Deluxe Room for a river view or choose an Executive Room for Executive Lounge access. \n\nHilton Mersin\n\nLook out over the Mediterranean from the seafront Mersin HiltonSA hotel. Get some exercise on the outdoor tennis courts before relaxing enjoying a cocktail in the pool at the Pool Bar. Do business in the 12th- floor Executive Lounge or in the 6 meeting rooms with space for up to 500. \n\nEnjoy local, Asian and international cuisine at the Mersin HiltonSA hotel. Our restaurant terraces overlook the Mediterranean. \n\nWork out in the gym or swimming pool at the Mersin HiltonSA hotel before unwinding in the health club’s sauna and massage. Mersin attractions are nearby, with museums and the famous Byzantine ruins, as is the beach and a full range of watersports. \n\nFrom a Hilton Room with city and sea views to a Junior Suite, all rooms have private balconies and internet access. Executive Rooms offer Executive Lounge access.", "experiences/18/jobEndedOn": "8-2005", "experiences/18/jobLocation": "Adana & Mersin, Turkiye", "experiences/18/jobLocationCountry": "US", "experiences/18/jobStartedOn": "6-2003", "experiences/18/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/18/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQGaUrNbmNf_sg/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1726853193572/hilton_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=iB1JGDdV-yJUje-GRQZx89ratKm7W7S0bKYqWhxOVZQ", "experiences/18/title": "Cluster Director of Business Development, Hilton Adana & Hilton Mersin", "experiences/19/companyId": "3055", "experiences/19/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/19/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/19/companyName": "Accor", "experiences/19/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/19/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/19/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/19/jobDescription": "Located within walking distance from the city centre, Celik Palas Bursa was established in 1935 by Ataturk, the founder of the Republic of Turkey. \n\nThe new Celik Palas Bursa is at present under development to become Swissotel The Celik Palas Bursa. \n\nDuring this development period, Raffles International will manage the existing Celik Palas Bursa. This hotel offers 156 guest rooms overlooking the city and the botanic gardens. \n\nHotel Çelik Palas has been established in 1935 following the founder of Turkish Republic, Mustafa Kemal Atatürk’s orders to build a thermal hotel in the city. \n\nFor its historical importance, the hotel is highly valued both by the local and the national community. \n\nApproaching the 1950s, in order to answer the increasing needs of the market, a new building was developed next to the existing one and began to operate in 1953. \n\nTherefore the hotel consists of two connecting buildings with the capacity of 156 rooms in total. \n\nHotel is no longer managed by Swissotel.", "experiences/19/jobEndedOn": "6-2003", "experiences/19/jobLocation": "Bursa, Turkiye", "experiences/19/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/19/jobStartedOn": "11-2002", "experiences/19/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/19/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/19/title": "Director of Rooms Division, Swissôtel Çelik Palas", "experiences/20/companyId": "3055", "experiences/20/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/20/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/20/companyName": "Accor", "experiences/20/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/20/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/20/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/20/jobDescription": "The Swissotel Boston is a modern, luxury hotel situated in downtown Boston, one block from Boston Common, and just 3 1/2 miles to Logan Airport. This centrally located hotel is also very convenient to major attractions, such as the Theatre District and the shops on Newbury Street. The Swissotel staff is cordial and well trained, catering to the individual needs of the guests. There is also a full service business center onsite, the Swissoffice.\n\n501 guest rooms, 22 floors, Sauna and/or steam room, Pets allowed, Restaurant(s) 'in house', Bar(s) 'in house', Airport transportation, Comfortable accommodations, Secure online reservations, Guaranteed lowest rates. \n\nThe Swissotel Boston's cozy and spacious guest rooms are beautiful and elegant, featuring a mixture of classic and chic. The furnishings are tastefully placed and feature bold mauve prints. Room service is available 24 hours a day from the in-house restaurant, CafÈ Suisse and there is also a lounge in the lobby. The Swissotel offers a fully equipped fitness facility with a sauna, whirlpool massage rooms and a sundeck. For recreation, the hotel also has an indoor swimming pool. The subway system's Green and Red Lines both stop at the nearby Park Street Station, offering guests easy access to the metropolitan area. The Swissotel Boston offers onsite fine dining, and it is convenient to shopping and entertainment venues.\n\nThe hotel is no longer operated by Swissotel and currently managed by Hyatt Regency (http://regencyboston.hyatt.com/en/hotel/home.html)", "experiences/20/jobEndedOn": "11-2002", "experiences/20/jobLocation": "Boston, Massachusetts, U.S.A.", "experiences/20/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/20/jobStartedOn": "1-2001", "experiences/20/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/20/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/20/title": "Front Office & Security Manager, Swissôtel Boston", "experiences/21/companyId": "3055", "experiences/21/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/21/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/accor/", "experiences/21/companyName": "Accor", "experiences/21/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/21/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:3055", "experiences/21/companyWebsite": "https://www.group.accor.com", "experiences/21/jobDescription": "The Swissotel Dalian is a luxurious 5 star hotel located in the downtown business and retail shopping district of Dalian, a 20 minutes drive from Dalian International Airport and a 5 minute ride from the main railway station. Swissotel Dalian provides convenient access to all parts of the city and development zone via the city's major network of wide roads and expressways. \n\nThe hotel is no longer operated by Swissotel", "experiences/21/jobEndedOn": "1-2001", "experiences/21/jobLocation": "Dalian, Liaoning, P.R. China", "experiences/21/jobLocationCountry": "FR", "experiences/21/jobStartedOn": "1-2000", "experiences/21/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/21/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQEpvDQjPca-eg/company-logo_400_400/B4EZfL86T0HIBg-/0/1751473432234/accor_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=p-3kNKncdGQ2BBqcIOej7odsRLl2IrBlsCQK-pNjXoM", "experiences/21/title": "Revenue Manager, Swissôtel Dalian", "experiences/22/companyId": "19051", "experiences/22/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/22/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/kempinski-hotels/", "experiences/22/companyName": "Kempinski Hotels", "experiences/22/companySize": "10001-0", "experiences/22/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:19051", "experiences/22/companyWebsite": "https://kempinski.com/", "experiences/22/jobDescription": "Çiragan Palace Kempinski Istanbul, once the home of Ottoman sultans, is dramatically situated on the shores of the Bosphorus. This incomparable view reflects the grandeur and glamour of the hotel itself, which is the only palace in Istanbul to have become a five-star hotel. It features a world of splendor where luxury and history blend in perfect harmony.  Fully restored to its former glory, the Çiragan Palace Kempinski combines Ottoman-era sophistication, with state-of-the-art technological amenities.   Located in the city center, just a 45-minute drive from Ataturk International Airport, the hotel offers its guests incomparable service and comfort. \n\nAll restaurants offer a balcony or terrace overlooking the Bosphorus.  In the palace wing, the elegant, award-winning Tugra Restaurant specializes in traditional Ottoman cuisine. In the hotel, Laledan Restaurant serves fish and mezze during lunch and dinner. The Gazebo Lo